body.description: Diono Cambria 2 XL, Dual Latch Connectors, 2-in-1 Belt Positioning Booster Seat, High-Back to Backless Booster, Space and Room to Grow, 7 Headrest Positions, 8 Years 1 Booster Seat, PinkCambria 2 XL Booster Seat combines space and room to grow, without compromising on safety or comfort. Suitable from 40 - 120 lb / 18 - 54 kg, expect 8 years of safety from just one booster seat. Awarded IIHS Best Bet Booster Seat, Cambria 2s extra wide design has plenty of room for your childs shoulders, hips, and legs. The ergonomic car seat base has been designed for complete child comfort and features 2x 2-in-1 fold-away cup holders and storage compartments to accommodate all your little one's cups, toys, and more on the move. Integrated LATCH connectors and front adjusters allow you to quickly tighten the booster car seat to the vehicle seat. The bright and bold covers allow your little one to arrive in style, with easy remove covers that can be machine washed and constructed from practical fabrics that can be wiped clean. When they are ready, the Cambria 2 transforms from a high-back booster to a backless booster seat offering two seats in one.
